=== WAR_ROOM_RECORDS ===
# id: 68
# title: The War Room Records
# chinese_title: 战争室记录
# category: Lore
# mode: dungeon

You stumble into what was clearly a military command center. Tactical displays show the positions of fleets long since destroyed or scattered. Battle plans, casualty reports, and intercepted communications paint a picture of a devastating conflict fought in this sector.

* [Study the tactical data]
  ~ gain_radical("刀")
  "战" (zhàn) — war, battle. The radical "刀" relates to weapons.
* [Search for salvageable military equipment]
  ~ gain_equipment
  "军" (jūn) — military, army
* [Download the communications intercepts]
  ~ gain_xp(20)
  "密" (mì) — secret, classified
* [Log the coordinates of the fallen fleets]
  ~ gain_gold(15)
  "亡" (wáng) — lost, fallen, dead
